\c 109
\s Umkhuleko wokucela impindiselo
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Nkulunkulu wendumiso yami\x + Dute. 10.21.\x*, ungathuli\x + Hlab. 28.1.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba umlomo wokhohlakeleyo lomlomo wenkohliso uvulekile umelene lami; bakhulume lami ngolimi lwamanga.
\v 3 Bangihanqa ngamazwi enzondo, balwa bemelene lami kungelasizatho\x + Hlab. 35.19.\x*.
\v 4 Esikhundleni sothando lwami bayizitha zami\x + Hlab. 38.20. 109.6.\x*, kodwa mina\x + Hlab. 120.7.\x* ngi\add se\add*mkhulekw\add eni\x + Hlab. 69.13.\x*\add*.
\v 5 Basebengibuyisela okubi esikhundleni sokuhle, lenzondo esikhundleni sothando lwami\x + Hlab. 35.12. 38.20.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Umise omubi\x + Hlab. 35.4-8. 69.22-28.\x* phezu kwakhe\x + Hlab. 55.12,13.\x*, loSathane\x + Zek. 3.1.\x* kame ngakwesokunene sakhe\x + Jobe 30.12.\x*\x + Zek. 3.1.\x*.
\v 7 Ekwahlulelweni kwakhe kaphume elecala\x + Hlab. 1.5.\x*; lomkhuleko wakhe ube yisono\x + Zaga 28.9.\x*.
\v 8 Insuku zakhe kazibe nlutshwana; omunye athathe isikhundla sakhe\x + Seb. 1.20. Joha. 17.12.\x*.
\v 9 Abantwana bakhe kabangabi loyise, lomkakhe \add abe\add* ngumfelokazi\x + Eks. 22.24.\x*.
\v 10 Abantwana bakhe kabazulazule\x + Hlab. 59.15.\x* bephanza \add isinkwa sabo\x + Zaga 20.4.\x*\add*, bacele bevela emanxiweni abo\x + Hlab. 37.25.\x*.
\v 11 Umebolekisi kabambe konke alakho\x + Hlab. 38.12.\x*, labezizweni baphange izithelo zomsebenzi wakhe\x + Isa. 5.17. Hlab. 128.2.\x*.
\v 12 Kungabi khona omelulela umusa\x + Hlab. 36.10. Neh. 9.30.\x*, futhi kungabi khona ozwela intandane zakhe\x + Jobe 5.4.\x*.
\v 13 Inzalo yakhe kayiqunywe\x + Hlab. 21.10.\x*, lebizo labo lesulwe esizukulwaneni esilandelayo\x + Zaga 10.7.\x*.
\v 14 Ububi baboyise bukhunjulwe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 20.5.\x*, lesono sikanina singesulwa\x + Neh. 4.5.\x*.
\v 15 Kabube phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njalonjalo, ukuze aqume ukukhunjulwa kwabo kusuke emhlabeni\x + Hlab. 34.16. Jobe 18.17.\x*.
\v 16 Ngenxa yokuthi wayengakhumbuli ukwenza umusa, kodwa wazingela umuntu ohluphekayo longumyanga\x + 109.22. Hlab. 86.1.\x*, lodabukileyo enhliziyweni uku\add m\add*bulala\x + Hlab. 34.18.\x*.
\v 17 Njengoba wathanda ukuqalekisa, ngakho kakwehlele kuye; njengoba wayengathandi ukubusisa, ngakho kakube khatshana laye\x + Hez. 35.6.\x*.
\v 18 Njengoba wagqoka isiqalekiso njengesigqoko sakhe\x + Hlab. 73.6.\x*, ngakho kakungene emibilini yakhe njengamanzi, lanjengamafutha emathanjeni akhe\x + Nani 5.22.\x*.
\v 19 Kakube kuye njengesembatho azembesa \add ngaso\add*, kube libhanti azibopha ngalo njalonjalo.
\v 20 Lokhu kube ngumvuzo wezitha zami ovela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lowalabo abakhuluma okubi ngomphefumulo wami\x + 109.6,29.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Kodwa wena, Jehova, Nkosi, ngenzela ngenxa yebizo lakho\x + Hlab. 25.11.\x*; ngoba umusa wakho ulungile, ngikhulule\x + Hlab. 69.16.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba mina ngiyisihlupheki lomyanga, lenhliziyo yami ilimele phakathi kwami\x + 109.22. Hlab. 86.1.\x*.
\v 23 Ngedlula njengesithunzi sisiba side\x + Hlab. 102.11. Jobe 14.2.\x*; ngizanyazanyiswe\x + Hlu. 16.20. Neh. 5.13.\x* njengesikhonyane\x + Jobe 39.20.\x*.
\v 24 Amadolo ami ayaxega ngokuzila ukudla\x + Heb. 12.12.\x*, lenyama yami isicakile iswela ukukhuluphala\x + Jobe 16.8.\x*.
\v 25 Mina sengibe lihlazo kubo\x + Hlab. 22.6.\x*, bengibona banikina ikhanda labo\x + Hlab. 22.7. Mat. 27.39. 2 Kho. 19.21.\x*.
\v 26 Ngisize, N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wami, ungisindise ngokomusa wakho\x + Hlab. 119.86.\x*.
\v 27 Ukuze bazi ukuthi lesi yisandla sakho; wena, N\nd kosi\nd*, ukwenzile.
\v 28 Kabathuke bona, kodwa wena ubusise\x + 2 Sam. 16.12.\x*; \add nxa\add* bevuka kabayangeke, kodwa inceku yakho kayithabe\x + Isa. 65.14.\x*.
\v 29 Izitha zami\x + 109.6,20.\x*\x + Hlab. 71.13.\x* kazigqokiswe ngehlazo\x + Jobe 8.22.\x*, kazizigoqele\x + Hlab. 71.13.\x* ngenhloni zazo njengesembatho\x + Jobe 8.22.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Ngizayibonga kakhulu iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlomo wami; njalo ngizayidumisa phakathi kwabanengi\x + Hlab. 22.25.\x*.
\v 31 Ngoba izakuma ngakwesokunene komyanga, uku\add m\add*sindisa kulabo abalahla umphefumulo wakhe\x + Hlab. 16.8. 109.6,7.\x*.
